This set of tools allow to work with FARGO3D outputs.

#---------------------------------------------------------
#			sources_f90
#---------------------------------------------------------

All f90 files are inside this directory. A brief description
is done in the next lines.

#avden.f90


#circumplanetary.f90


#create_names.f90


#input_file.f90


#readbinaryall.f90


#reader.f90


#trans_coords.f90
Inside this file there are all the subroutines that transform
the fargo output files into csv files.
These subroutines are called in main routines such as
trans_to_csv.f90

#trans_to_csv.f90
This file takes the fargo output files and transforms them to
csv files.



